WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.133 --> 00:00:02.500
Tell the Empress to calm down.

2
00:00:02.566 --> 00:00:05.000
The Emperor really stayed in the Nourishing Heart Palace all night yesterday.

3
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:06.600
He didn’t come out at all.

4
00:00:07.333 --> 00:00:08.266
Please calm down, Your Highness.

5
00:00:11.966 --> 00:00:13.433
Nourishing Heart Palace.

6
00:00:14.700 --> 00:00:17.366
That’s a treatment even I have never experienced.

7
00:00:18.366 --> 00:00:21.766
Do you think the Emperor is tired of me?

8
00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:24.200
Why would you think that, Your Highness?

9
00:00:24.266 --> 00:00:26.100
When the Emperor first ascended the throne,

10
00:00:26.100 --> 00:00:27.366
he made you a Consort

11
00:00:27.366 --> 00:00:29.500
despite having to quarrel with the Empress Dowager and the officials.

12
00:00:29.533 --> 00:00:32.633
Such an honor is unique to you.

13
00:00:33.533 --> 00:00:34.833
That is true.

14
00:00:35.166 --> 00:00:38.200
But what is the true background of the identity that Prince Duan gave me?

15
00:00:38.300 --> 00:00:40.933
It has confused even the rules of the Qin family.

16
00:00:40.933 --> 00:00:41.733
Yes, Your Highness.

17
00:00:41.733 --> 00:00:43.500
You must not let an outsider's favor

18
00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:44.400
drive a wedge between you and the Emperor.

19
00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:45.366
It’s not worth it.

20
00:00:45.366 --> 00:00:48.633
But last night, in front of so many people,

21
00:00:48.700 --> 00:00:50.166
the Emperor embarrassed me.

22
00:00:50.166 --> 00:00:50.800
Your Highness.

23
00:00:50.800 --> 00:00:53.333
I actually think the Emperor was protecting you.

24
00:00:53.333 --> 00:00:55.800
Protecting me? Are you blind?

25
00:00:55.933 --> 00:00:57.700
He was clearly protecting Consort Rong.

26
00:00:58.466 --> 00:01:01.166
Your Highness, listen to my analysis.

27
00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:03.166
Previously, the Emperor argued with the officials and the Empress Dowager

28
00:01:03.166 --> 00:01:05.166
over the selection of concubines.

29
00:01:05.333 --> 00:01:06.966
The Emperor’s protection of you

30
00:01:06.966 --> 00:01:08.866
increased their hatred towards you.

31
00:01:08.866 --> 00:01:10.833
The Empress Dowager’s birthday banquet is approaching.

32
00:01:10.866 --> 00:01:12.400
Now that the Emperor’s position is unstable,

33
00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:13.700
if the Empress Dowager and the officials

34
00:01:14.066 --> 00:01:16.700
strive to depose you,

35
00:01:17.700 --> 00:01:19.400
even if the Emperor protects you,

36
00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:20.466
it won’t help.

37
00:01:20.466 --> 00:01:21.466
Yes, Your Highness.

38
00:01:21.700 --> 00:01:23.533
Now, with the addition of Consort Rong,

39
00:01:23.533 --> 00:01:26.266
the Empress Dowager and the officials’ attention will shift.

40
00:01:26.333 --> 00:01:28.200
And I’ve specially inquired,

41
00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:30.166
the Emperor spent the whole night in his robe.

42
00:01:30.166 --> 00:01:31.633
He didn’t even touch Consort Rong.

43
00:01:32.300 --> 00:01:34.466
It’s truly worth noting.

44
00:01:36.933 --> 00:01:39.700
The dragon bone soup will be sent to the Nourishing Heart Palace today.

45
00:01:40.900 --> 00:01:42.933
Rest assured, it will be delivered by the fifteenth day.

46
00:01:42.933 --> 00:01:44.166
I will remember.

47
00:01:44.500 --> 00:01:47.400
Go and bring me paper and ink.

48
00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:54.800
The Emperor has indeed acted as you expected.

49
00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:58.166
Consort Yan has been secretly sending messages outside the palace.

50
00:01:58.466 --> 00:02:01.066
The person has already been secretly detained.

51
00:02:01.066 --> 00:02:03.600
It seems they had already conspired together before entering the palace.

52
00:02:03.600 --> 00:02:05.666
It appears Prince Duan has been secretly planning

53
00:02:05.666 --> 00:02:07.400
during the past three years he was away.

54
00:02:08.366 --> 00:02:10.333
Dispose of that person who is a threat.

55
00:02:10.333 --> 00:02:11.266
Handle it cleanly.

56
00:02:11.266 --> 00:02:13.100
Do not alert the enemy.
